    <section class="faq" id="faq">

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <!-- Voice Search Optimized Answers -->
      <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 24px;padding:20px;background:rgba(210,171,111,0.1);border-radius:12px;border-left:4px solid var(--brand)">
        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6;font-weight:600">Quick Answers:</p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6">
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>How much?</strong> $499/day (1 day), $449/day (2 days), $399/day (3 days), $349/day (5 days), $2,000 (1 week)</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>Where?</strong> All Metro Atlanta areas: Buckhead, Midtown, Downtown, Sandy Springs, Alpharetta, Roswell, Milton, Johns Creek, Dunwoody, Vinings, ATL Airport</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>Age requirement?</strong> 25+ (call if 21‚Äì24)</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>Rating?</strong> 5.0 based on 7+ verified reviews</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>Horsepower?</strong> 385 hp, 0‚Äì60 mph in 4.5 seconds</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><strong>Deposit?</strong> Refundable security deposit required</p>
        </div>
      </div>



      <details>

        <summary>What are the rental requirements?</summary>

        <p>Valid US driver's license, major credit card, and full-coverage insurance that extends to the rental. Minimum age <strong>25</strong> (call if 21‚Äì24). Additional verification may apply.</p>

      </details>



      <details>

        <summary>How does insurance work?</summary>

        <p>Renter must carry full-coverage auto insurance (liability, comp, collision) that extends to the rental. We verify coverage and limits before release. Additional drivers can be added with license & insurance.</p>

      </details>



      <details>

        <summary>Is there a deposit?</summary>

        <p>Yes, a refundable security deposit is held at checkout and released after return and inspection. Fuel, cleaning, tolls, tickets, and over-miles are billed as applicable.</p>

      </details>



      <details>

        <summary>Do you deliver to ATL Airport or hotels?</summary>

        <p>Yes. Delivery is available across <strong>all Metro Atlanta areas</strong> including Buckhead, Midtown, Downtown, Sandy Springs, Alpharetta, Roswell, Milton, Johns Creek, Dunwoody, Vinings, and ATL Airport; pricing is based on distance/time. Hotel deliveries require ID and payment verification.</p>

      </details>



      <details>

        <summary>Can I rent for a photoshoot or brand campaign?</summary>

        <p>Yes. The vehicle is content-friendly with professional handling and clear guidelines. We've worked with numerous photographers and content creators.</p>

      </details>



      <details>

        <summary>What's your cancellation policy?</summary>

        <p>Reservations are <strong>non-refundable</strong>. At our discretion, we may issue a future credit. Please review your confirmation for details.</p>

      </details>

    </section>



